title: I AM
lyrics:
I AM I AM I AM I AM
I AM
Eodiseodo bonjeog eobsji
Guess, Who we are

Amuna ttalawa ige nuguya eodiseodo bonjeog eobsji

Mom-eul pul-eo naleul jal neukkyeo meolibuteo balkkeutkkaji

Saeng-gagji moshaessdeon gyeongheom-eul ani eojjeomyeon uju jeopyeon neomeoleul

Jigeumbuteo du nun gamgo nawa gat-i hana dul ses swis



Amu uisim hajima naleul tonghae saelo taeeona

Sangsangdo mos hal sesang-i ol geol naleul da boyeojulge

I AM



Jeo eodum sog-e seonmyeonghaejin gil-eul ttalaseo

Naleul ttalawa Baby



Oh! Oh! The brave new world

Jal deul-eobwa ige balo naya
